  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Creation of proper learning environment for informal education</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Vytvorenie vhodn&#xE9;ho vyu&#x10D;ovacieho priestoru na neformalne vzdel&#xE1;vanie</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Cie&#x13E;om projektu je zlep&#x161;i&#x165; &#x161;tandardy na neform&#xE1;lne vzdel&#xE1;vanie, &#xFA;rove&#x148; vzdelania det&#xED; a podmienok pre usklad&#x148;ovanie u&#x10D;ebn&#xFD;ch pom&#xF4;cok v centre ako aj zlep&#x161;i&#x165; form&#xE1;lne vzdel&#xE1;vanie det&#xED; a celkov&#xFA; atmosf&#xE9;ru v triede.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of the project is to improve the standards of the informal education, the level of children&#x2019;s education and the conditions of the learning materials storage in the centre as well as prepare the children better for formal education and provide the child environment friendly atmosphere in the class.</narrative>
  </description>
